Package: crafty-enormousbook
Version: 18
Revision: 1
Depends: crafty
Replaces: crafty, crafty-smallbook, crafty-largebook
Source:  ftp://ftp.cis.uab.edu/pub/hyatt/common/enormous/a.zip
Source2: ftp://ftp.cis.uab.edu/pub/hyatt/common/enormous/b.zip
Source3: ftp://ftp.cis.uab.edu/pub/hyatt/common/enormous/c.zip
Source4: ftp://ftp.cis.uab.edu/pub/hyatt/common/enormous/d.zip
Source5: ftp://ftp.cis.uab.edu/pub/hyatt/common/enormous/e.zip
NoSourceDirectory: true
CompileScript: <<
cat ?.PGN>book.txt
rm ?.PGN
echo "book create book.txt 60 2 50" | crafty
<<
InstallScript: <<
mkdir -p %i/lib/crafty
/usr/bin/install -c -m 444 book.bin %i/lib/crafty
chmod a+w %i/lib/crafty/book.bin
<<
Description: Enormous (100M) opening book for Crafty
DescDetail: <<
This is an enormously large opening book provided for crafty. You will need
several gigabytes of free disk space to build it, although the finished book
is only about 100M.
<<
